### Notes

- Presenter notes (only visible in presenter mode)
- Example: `html\`<${Notes}>These are presenter notes</${Notes}>\``

### Progress

- Slide progress indicators
- Props: `size`, `color`
- Example: `html\`<${Progress} size={30} color="primary" />\``

